=Generate a pre-call diagnostic brief for this prospect:

Name: {{ $('📋 Parse Booking Data').first().json.fullName }}
Call time: {{ $('📋 Parse Booking Data').first().json.formattedDate }}

Intake Form Responses:
- Revenue model: {{ $json['What is your company revenue model?'] || 'Not provided' }}
- Team size: {{ $json['How many employees or contractors are on your team?'] || 'Not provided' }}
- Biggest time drain: {{ $json['Where does your team lose the most time each week?'] || 'Not provided' }}
- AI experience: {{ $json['Have you tried AI tools before? What happened?'] || 'Not provided' }}
- 90-day win: {{ $json['What would a win look like 90 days from now?'] || 'Not provided' }}
- Tech stack: {{ $json['What is your current tech stack?'] || 'Not provided' }}

Generate a brief with these exact sections:

## Company Snapshot
(2-3 sentences on what you know about their situation based on responses)

## Primary Pain Points
(Rank top 3 by ROI impact with a one-line explanation each)

## Quick Wins (30 Days)
(2-3 specific workflows IntraWeb could automate immediately)

## Diagnostic Focus Areas
(What the $10K assessment would investigate for this company)

## Cost of Inaction
(Specific framing of what staying the same costs them — time, money, competitive position)

## Suggested Talking Points
(3-4 specific questions John should ask on this call to qualify and advance the deal)

Be direct and specific. No fluff.

